    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine currently struggles to start and runs roughly, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping between gears. Visually, the car has significant body damage, including deep rust patches on the rocker panels and several large dents. The interior is heavily worn with torn seats and several non-functional electrical components, including the radio and power windows. It is not currently in roadworthy condition and will require significant mechanical work and investment.",
