    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it still has that new car smell and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it from day one, keeping it garage-kept and meticulously cleaned. It drives like a dream and is ready to hit the road today. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative specimen of the S54-powered icon, maintained to a rigorous standard. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a fully overhauled VANOS system and treated rod bearings, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency and mechanical longevity. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via a factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement, mitigating the platform's known structural fatigue points. The exterior retains its factory luster with no signs of oxidation, while the interior features pristine Nappa leather with minimal bolster wear. All suspension kinematics have been refreshed with OEM+ components for sharpened turn-in and lateral stability. This is a collector-grade driver's car with zero deferred maintenance and exceptional mechanical transparency.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Full service records included. Garage kept. Smoke-free interior.",
      "price": 44000.0,
