    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating\u2014absolutely zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition, with the premium leather bolsters showing no signs of wear and the original floor mats appearing untouched. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history and a recent inspection confirming peak performance. From the pristine alloy wheels to the spotless engine bay, every detail reflects a life of obsessive care. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership floor.",
